sentence: The Home Depot Inc.HD , the world's largest home improvement retailer, released fourth-quarter fiscal 20Array5 results, wherein earnings of $Array.Array7 a share came ahead of the Zacks Consensus Estimate of $Array.Array0 and jumped ArrayArray.4% year over year.
